"1 cup rolled oats","1 cup roughly chopped hazelnuts","1/4 cup plus 1 Tbsp. packed light brown sugar","4 tablespoons cold unsalted butter, cut into pieces","1/4 teaspoon salt","4  pears (about 2 lb. total), such as Bartlett, each cored and cut into 8 wedges","1 1/2 cups pitted sour cherries, thawed if frozen or drained if canned","1 teaspoon cornstarch","1 tablespoon lemon juice","  Whole-milk Greek yogurt and honey, for serving, optional"